  <description type="2" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Contribute to Common Humanitarian Fund (CHF)</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The armed conflict is increasingly intense during 2019, at the same time as the country has been hit hard by drought. As a direct consequence, the number of people in need of humanitarian aid has almost doubled and now amounts to 6.3 million people according to the UN. This is met with a grant of DKK 35 million to the UN Humanitarian Country Fund, which is a key tool for prioritized efforts through the UN as well as international and local civil society organizations.
https://www.unocha.org/afghanistan/about-ahf</narrative>
